---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/sections/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Heading from '../components/ui/Heading.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services | Geek Life Development"
  description="Explore website projects, practical business tools, and ongoing support delivered with clear scope and reliable communication."
>
  <Hero
    title="Services built for small businesses that want clear, reliable results"
    subtitle="We help business owners in Ozaukee County, Milwaukee, and beyond launch professional websites and keep them improving over time."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Get a quote', href: '/contact' }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'See pricing', href: '/pricing' }}
    accent={false}
  />

  <Section>
    <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Websites"
        title="Our core service: clear, professional websites"
        subtitle="Your site should build trust quickly, explain what you do, and make it easy for people to reach out."
      />

      <Card hover={false}>
        <p class="label-mono text-slate-500">Typical website engagement includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li>• Clear page structure and strong business messaging</li>
          <li>• A polished experience across phone, tablet, and desktop</li>
          <li>• Search-friendly setup for long-term visibility</li>
          <li>• Ongoing support options for updates and improvements</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-4xl space-y-4">
      <p>
        This is a strong fit for businesses that want a professional online presence without constant rework.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">We focus on practical scope and dependable delivery.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="muted">
    <div class="space-y-10">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Simple apps"
        title="Business tools for clear, specific needs"
        subtitle="When your team needs more than a brochure site, we can add practical tools that support daily operations."
      />

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Client or member areas</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Private pages for clients, members, or internal teams.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Reporting views</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Simple reporting screens that highlight the information your team needs most.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Scheduling systems</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Booking and availability tools that make scheduling easier for staff and customers.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Internal workflows</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Simple systems that reduce repetitive work and improve consistency.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Form-based processes</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">Better intake and handoff flows for leads, requests, and client updates.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <p>We keep scope focused on the most valuable business outcome first, then expand as needed.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Larger custom platforms are scoped as separate engagements.</p>
        <Button href="/contact">Discuss your idea</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="grid items-start gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Ongoing support"
        title="Ongoing support that keeps your site current"
        subtitle="After launch, we provide steady monthly support so your website stays polished, accurate, and useful."
      />

      <Card hover={false}>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li>• Monthly updates and quality checks</li>
          <li>• Content and layout improvements</li>
          <li>• Hosting guidance and launch support</li>
          <li>• Ongoing performance and reliability reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 max-w-4xl">
      Most clients get better long-term results with ongoing support than one-time updates every few months.
    </p>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="muted">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <Heading
        eyebrow="Boundaries"
        title="Clear boundaries, better projects"
        subtitle="Clear boundaries protect timelines, budgets, and outcomes for everyone involved."
      />
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No vague scope</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No unclear deliverables</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No surprise process changes</p>
        </Card>
        <Card hover={false} class="p-5">
          <p class="font-medium text-slate-900">No rushed project delivery</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="dark">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-white">When communication is clear, projects move smoothly.</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <Button href="/contact" size="lg">Get a quote</Button>
        <Button href="/work" size="lg" variant="secondary">View work</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>